<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head.ejs') %>
        <style>
            @media (min-width: 1024px) {
                .fixed-latest-blog {
                    position: sticky;
                    top: 1rem;
                }
            }

            /* Custom CSS */
            /* Adjusting heading margins */
            .content-heading {
                margin-top: 3rem;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }

            /* Styling the team member cards */
            .team-member {
                transition: all 0.3s;
            }

            .team-member:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }
        </style>
        </style>
</head>

<body class=" bg-slate-700">
    <header>
        <%- include("./partials/nav.ejs") %>
    </header>
    <h1 class="text-slate-950 text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">.</h1>
    <!-- main  -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">

            <div class="sm:flex items-center max-w-screen-xl">
                <div class="sm:w-1/2 p-10">
                    <div class="image object-center text-center">
                        <img src="https://i.imgur.com/WbQnbas.png">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="sm:w-1/2 p-5">
                    <div class="text">
                        <span class="text-gray-500 border-b-2 border-indigo-600 uppercase">About us</span>
                        <h2 class="my-4 font-bold text-3xl  sm:text-4xl ">About <span class="text-indigo-600">
                               Blogify</span>
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">
                            Welcome to Blogify, your go-to destination for insightful articles, tips, and resources on
                            all things
                            blogging and content creation. Our mission is to empower bloggers of all levels with the
                            knowledge and
                            tools they need to succeed in the digital world.
                            At Blogify, we believe in the power of storytelling and the impact it can have on
                            individuals and
                            communities. Whether you're a seasoned blogger looking to refine your craft or a newbie
                            eager to
                            embark on your blogging journey, we've got you covered.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Team section -->
            <div class="mt-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 content-heading">Meet Our Team</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-8">
                    <!-- Team member card -->
                    <div class=" w-full bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md team-member flex flex-col items-center">
                        <img src="../images/nk.png" alt="Aryan Singh" class="rounded-full w-24 h-24 object-cover object-center mb-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Aryan Singh</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">Founder</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
                            Hello, I'm Aryan Singh, the creator and founder of Blogify, a dynamic platform where you can share your thoughts, ideas, and stories with the world. At Blogify, we believe in the power of words and the importance of community. Our website allows you to post blogs on any topic, giving you the freedom to express yourself and connect with like-minded individuals. Readers can not only enjoy diverse content but also engage in meaningful discussions, fostering a vibrant and interactive online community. Join us at Blogify, where your voice matters, and every story finds its audience..I embarked on a journey to establish Blogify as a go-to platform
                            for bloggers of all levels.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Add more team members -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>